Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,00:02:25.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's not for here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,00:02:27.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff #2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,00:02:28.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What does this key open?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,00:02:30.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,00:02:45.87,Caption,,0,0,0,,Totally                                                       Dirty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,00:02:51.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Looks like the end of the line \Nfor you, Taromaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,00:02:53.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So accept your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,00:02:56.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,00:02:57.20,Caption,,0,0,0,,Splat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,00:03:11.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,00:03:15.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My, you two, don't you know running in the halls...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,00:03:18.33,Caption,,0,0,0,,Rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,00:03:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...is a no-no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,00:03:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,00:03:24.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I finally caught you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,00:03:27.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're filthy. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,00:03:31.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Taromaru somehow got out of his collar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,00:03:35.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and when I found him, he was \Nswimming in the pond on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,00:03:37.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Pond?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,00:03:39.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, the water tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,00:03:41.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He was swimming in that filthy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,00:03:44.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I was gonna give him a bath, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,00:03:46.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So you chased after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,00:03:48.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and that's how you ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,00:03:49.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,00:03:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,00:03:55.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,00:04:00.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of the hallway, \Nso you and Taromaru go get cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.58,00:04:02.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,00:04:05.75,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Jeez, the hallway's all dirty, \Nand it's all your fault, Taromaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,00:04:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,00:04:13.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,00:04:16.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot! I forgot to take off my boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,00:04:29.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How does the water feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,00:04:33.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stay still now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,00:04:35.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll be over real quick if you don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,00:04:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on, you're almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,00:04:44.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, you're totally soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,00:04:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,00:04:47.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,00:04:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,00:04:56.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm okay, it's my job, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,00:04:57.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,00:05:04.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, I just saved you from a lotta trouble, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,00:05:06.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Show some gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,00:05:10.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't jump on my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,00:05:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,00:05:16.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I think I really do need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,00:05:18.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,00:05:20.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, but leave the shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,00:05:22.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,00:05:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,00:05:30.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you hold him down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,00:05:32.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,00:05:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, round two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,00:06:08.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,00:06:07.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, wa... Mii-kun, hold on, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,00:06:14.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,00:06:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It'll be over quickly if you don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,00:06:18.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,W-well yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,00:06:21.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun, could you be a little more gentle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,00:06:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll catch a cold if I don't dry you off all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,00:06:26.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then let's use the hair dryer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,00:06:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't. Taromaru's using it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,00:06:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Awww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,00:06:44.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Taromaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,00:06:45.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,that's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,00:06:48.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't play with Yuki's hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,00:06:51.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks, Kurumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,00:06:53.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'd get sick if you ate this dirty thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,00:06:55.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Kurumi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,00:06:58.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, I washed it, it's not dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,00:07:02.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad all of your laundry dried quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,00:07:03.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,00:07:07.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The sun's really shining down on us today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,00:07:09.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Which means it's really hot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,00:07:11.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,00:07:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,00:07:16.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,00:07:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,00:07:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop lounging around in that and put on your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,00:07:23.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,00:07:28.37,Caption,,0,0,0,,Let's all graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,00:07:28.37,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Everyone write 100 pages!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,00:07:28.37,Caption3,,0,0,0,,I can't write that many!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,00:07:28.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can't be lazy like this all the time, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,00:07:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, you're all graduating high school next year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,00:07:31.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Graduation Album
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,00:07:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,00:07:36.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Worry about tomorrow tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,00:07:38.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,00:07:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to do the things you can today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,00:07:46.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,We're so lucky to have all the equipment \Nwe need here at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,00:07:49.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We should make the most of them right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,00:07:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For our future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,00:07:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of things we can do before graduation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,00:07:59.33,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,and lots of things we have to do \Nbefore we can graduate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,00:08:01.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,so let's make sure they get done!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,00:08:02.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,00:08:05.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There sure are lots of things we can start preparing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,00:08:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Plus we've gotta study.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,00:08:12.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we should ask Megu-nee for advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,00:08:16.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you going to go to college, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,00:08:19.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Well, lately I've been thinking \NI'd just start working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,00:08:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, I wouldn't have to take any tests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,00:08:24.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are employment exams you'd have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,00:08:25.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,00:08:27.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hear finding a job's really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,00:08:28.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,00:08:31.87,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Well maybe I'll just stay a \Nhigh school student forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,00:08:33.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You really are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,00:08:36.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll drop down to your class, Mii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,00:08:37.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,00:08:41.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,College or finding a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,00:08:44.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,00:08:45.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,00:08:47.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,00:08:49.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,00:08:51.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eh, maybe go for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,00:08:57.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,So you want a job you can do \Nwith Mr. Shovel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,00:08:59.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you be a little more imaginative?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,00:09:03.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,And in this recession, they'd be \Nlooking for more men than women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,00:09:05.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,00:09:07.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are other opportunities!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,00:09:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,L-like finding a permanent job,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,00:09:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,or g-getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,00:09:16.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,00:09:18.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To Mr. Shovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,00:09:20.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you so fixated on my shovel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,00:09:24.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do, Miki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,00:09:28.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,00:09:36.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's still hazy, so I don't really have a solid idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,00:09:42.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,00:09:44.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I hope one day, we all will find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,00:09:49.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,00:09:52.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.16,00:09:53.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's start a club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,00:09:56.66,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think we'll be more motivated \Nhaving goals to pursue,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,00:09:59.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,rather than just living out our days normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,00:10:03.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes. I thought about having classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,00:10:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but a club is much more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,00:10:07.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What club will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,00:10:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,00:10:11.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a club about living at school, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,00:10:16.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The School Living Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,00:10:20.83,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,How wonderful, we came up with something \Nwithout needing to brainstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,00:10:24.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I already know what kind of things you like, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,00:10:26.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Since your taste is the same as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,00:10:28.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,00:10:30.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,00:10:36.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,Club Application Form
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,00:10:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,00:10:39.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm counting on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,00:10:42.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,School Living Club President!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,00:10:46.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm the president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,00:10:50.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think you're the best one for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,00:10:55.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright. I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,00:11:06.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Student Council Room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,00:11:19.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,School Living Club
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,00:11:19.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,00:11:23.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone line up in front of the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,00:11:26.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's take a commemorative picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,00:11:33.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, one, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,00:11:37.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,00:11:38.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wakasa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,00:11:40.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,00:11:41.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,00:11:43.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got to get a picture with our advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,00:11:46.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee, come stand over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,00:11:48.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Takeya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,00:11:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,00:11:54.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,00:12:01.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You scared me there, Takeya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,00:12:03.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,00:12:06.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah, the picture's coming out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,00:12:08.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did I blink?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,00:12:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Should we take another?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,00:12:11.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,00:12:15.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're in there just fine, Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,00:12:29.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff #2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,00:12:38.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai, you're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,00:12:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,00:12:45.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,00:12:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't sleep either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,00:12:50.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,00:12:52.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Something's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,00:12:55.83,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,00:12:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,00:13:00.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,00:13:06.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,00:13:10.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,How we're so lucky to have all the equipment \Nwe need here at this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,00:13:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,00:13:15.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It made me realize something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,00:13:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a little too lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,00:13:24.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I went around the school again to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,00:13:27.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The solar panels,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,00:13:30.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,the rainwater collection tank \Nand the water purifier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,00:13:32.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,the vegetable garden on the roof \Nand emergency food stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,00:13:37.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's like the school was built specifically \Nto allow people to live in its walls indefinitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,00:13:38.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's just-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,00:13:40.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,00:13:42.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's a silly thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,00:13:46.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I just can't stop thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,00:13:50.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,00:14:02.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,00:14:04.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,00:14:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,00:14:13.62,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,The equipment and facilities \Non their own aren't that rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,00:14:18.12,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I'd expect a brand-new office building \Nto have at least one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,00:14:23.91,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,But for all of them to be together in one place, \Nit's a completely different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,00:14:28.66,Caption,,0,0,0,,Staff #2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,00:14:28.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is that the same key from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,00:14:34.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Sakura
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,00:14:29.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,00:14:34.16,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling this key is a clue \Nto solving some of the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,00:14:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was going to talk to everyone about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,00:14:42.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you come with me for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,00:14:59.00,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,I thought we'd already looked in \Nthe teacher's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,00:15:03.25,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yes, we checked here first, \Nsince the key said "staff" on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,00:15:06.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So what's the point of coming here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,00:15:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'd only taken a look around Megu-nee's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,00:15:14.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We'll do a more thorough search tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,00:15:17.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,For tonight, we can stop when we get sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,00:15:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,00:15:21.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,00:15:25.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's split the room and see what we can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,00:15:27.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,00:15:58.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this Megu-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,00:16:03.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What're you girls doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,00:16:06.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,00:16:09.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,00:16:13.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I woke up 'cause I had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,00:16:16.37,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Then I noticed you two weren't there \Nand I kinda panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,00:16:18.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I'm sorry, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,00:16:22.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sakura-sensei asked us to look for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,00:16:26.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Th-that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,00:16:30.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She wanted us to find out what this key goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,00:16:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, a treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,00:16:35.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,00:16:48.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,00:16:51.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,00:16:56.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,00:16:58.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,00:17:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Where did that stuffed animal come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,00:17:01.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,00:17:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what to say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,00:17:05.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please put it back where you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,00:17:07.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,00:17:12.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,00:17:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,00:17:20.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,00:17:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,00:17:26.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Have you completely forgotten about the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,00:17:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This sleeping bag is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,00:17:29.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can walk around in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,00:17:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,00:17:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,00:17:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,00:17:43.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,00:17:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,00:17:47.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mii-kun! Shoot me with that camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,00:17:55.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and record, yo, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,00:17:58.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mic check, mic check, one two, one two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,00:18:00.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hello, all you at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,00:18:02.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Can ya hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,00:18:04.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,00:18:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You realize this isn't a video camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,00:18:08.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,00:18:10.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take your picture, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,00:18:11.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,00:18:13.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,00:18:19.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mii-kun, you gotta give me some warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,00:18:22.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You told me to get a shot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,00:18:33.58,Caption,,0,0,0,,Slap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,00:18:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's just paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,00:18:36.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Senpai, calm down. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,00:18:37.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,00:18:40.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,00:18:42.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is awesome! Super awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,00:18:44.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's call it "The Awesome Camera"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,00:18:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's already called an instant camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,00:18:48.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Look, Ri-san, isn't it awesome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,00:18:51.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ri-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,00:18:54.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,00:18:55.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,00:19:01.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Remember when we took a picture \Nof all of us with this camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,00:19:04.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And what happened after?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,00:19:07.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ri-san, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,00:19:09.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,J-jeez, Yuki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,00:19:10.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,00:19:14.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai's mad at you \Nbecause you're playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,00:19:15.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,00:19:20.29,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,It's getting late, so let's hurry up and \Nfind something this key might unlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,00:19:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,00:19:25.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai, that wasn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,00:19:27.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,00:19:29.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It happened right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,00:19:34.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Right after we took this picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,00:19:36.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Megu-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,00:19:45.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are more of them lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,00:19:48.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, there wasn't anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,00:19:50.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,00:19:53.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shall we leave things here for today and get to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,00:19:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,00:19:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,00:19:58.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,00:20:01.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think we already looked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,00:20:04.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,00:20:11.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There was a hidden compartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,00:20:13.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And there's a safe inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,00:20:15.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What a surprise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,00:20:17.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, a big surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,00:20:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,00:20:22.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You really are amazing, Yuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,00:20:25.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you're welcome, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,00:20:28.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,00:20:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,00:20:57.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A DVD to use in class and a list.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,00:21:00.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.45,00:21:03.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is this all Megu-nee wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,00:21:04.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,00:21:08.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then I'm gonna go tell Megu-nee we got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,00:21:12.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Guess it was nothing after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,00:21:13.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yuri-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,00:21:16.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,CONFIDENTIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,00:21:16.00,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Faculty Emergency Evacuation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.04,00:21:16.00,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,CONFIDENTIAL
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption2,,0,0,0,,Faculty Emergency Evacuation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption3,,0,0,0,,Manual
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption4,,0,0,0,,Only open this manual when:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption5,,0,0,0,,-  The principal or other official has ordered it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption6,,0,0,0,,-  An A-1 warning has been issued
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,00:21:19.00,Caption7,,0,0,0,,-  No outside communication has been received for more than 10 days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,00:21:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,00:21:25.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Could you hurry and go wake up Kurumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,00:21:37.41,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,A biological weapon can potentially cause more \Ndamage than anticipated depending on its composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,00:21:41.08,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,A pandemic, where the biological agent \Nspreads rapidly and uncontrollably,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,00:21:43.70,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,can result in the event that \Ncontainment measures fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,00:21:46.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Complete isolation is the key to survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,00:21:48.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those in contact with infected must also be isolated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,00:21:50.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sustaining the means of propagating the human race
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,00:21:52.95,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,is an act much more important \Nthan the lives of individuals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,00:21:56.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hundreds of thousands of lives are in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.95,00:22:01.45,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Generosity and sympathy are \Nno longer virtues in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,00:22:07.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A biological weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,00:22:11.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on a damn sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,00:22:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,00:22:14.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,00:22:22.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We found what you were looking for, Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,00:22:24.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was really hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,00:22:26.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,00:22:28.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we found this really cute stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,00:22:31.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I shoulda brought it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,00:22:33.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll show it to you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,00:22:45.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Akaneiro ni kimi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.41,00:22:52.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,Nani o kangaeteita no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,00:22:58.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Mabuta ippai namida o tamete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,00:23:03.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Gomakashiteita kirei da ne to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,00:23:06.62,Caption,,0,0,0,,Utagai mo naku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,00:23:14.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,Konna hibi ga tsuzuite ikunda tte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,00:23:20.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Zutto omotteita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,00:23:24.41,Caption,,0,0,0,,Miageta sora wa tooku tooku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.41,00:23:27.50,Caption,,0,0,0,,Bokura mitsumeteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,00:23:32.75,Caption,,0,0,0,,Tada shizuka ni kawaranai mama
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.08,00:23:36.12,Caption,,0,0,0,,Maigo no te to te nigirishimeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,00:23:39.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,Mou samishiku wa nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,00:23:44.54,Caption,,0,0,0,,Owaru sekai mukou gishi eto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,00:23:52.45,Caption,,0,0,0,,Bokura no yoake ga mieru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,00:23:55.29,Caption,,0,0,0,,Mieru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,00:24:02.00,Caption,,0,0,0,,Waratte
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,00:24:07.08,Caption,,0,0,0,,Next Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,00:24:08.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,00:24:09.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If it's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.66,00:24:10.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When it's hot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,00:24:12.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, calm down, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.66,00:24:13.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But it's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,00:24:15.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Days like this, you just gotta-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.16,00:24:16.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tell horror stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,00:24:17.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,00:24:21.04,Caption,,0,0,0,,Vacation Day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.54,00:24:21.04,Subtitle2,,0,0,0,,Next time on School-Live, episode 9: \N"Vacation Day!"
